high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the tub.
Pick up the leftmost purple rag out of the tub.
Turn right and walk over to the sink, the turn right and walk up to the toilet.
Put the purple rag on the left side of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the tub.
Pick up the purple rag out of the tub.
Walk back over to the toilet behind you.
Put the purple rag on top of the toilet tank to the right of the rag that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two purple rags to the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the tub.
Pick up the purple wash rag that is on your left.
With the wash rag in hand turn and go to the side of the toilet that is next to the sink.
Place the wash rag on the back of the toilet right behind the handle on the toilet.
Turn and go to the tub.
Pick up the wash rag that is in the middle of the tub.
Turn and go to the side of the toilet that is on the side where the sink is.
Place the wash rag behind the other wash rag that is on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move two wash rags to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the tub
Grab a rag out of the tub
Turn around and go to the left of the toilet
Put the rag on top of the toilet
Turn around and go to the tub
Grab a rag out of the tub
Turn around and go to the left of the toilet
Put the rag on the toilet
anns.task_desc: Putting two rags on top of the toilet
